{"type":"message","id":"50928dab","parentId":"2931fbba","timestamp":"2026-02-11T19:27:13.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Examining Docker Performance**\n\nI've started the assessment by planning to list the running Docker containers using `docker ps`, to pinpoint the `DMarket-Bot` stack's services. Following that, I'll move on to inspect container statistics, and then I will monitor CPU/RAM utilization and stability. This seems like a good path forward.\n\n\n**Identifying Target Containers**\n\nNow, I'm working on the initial step. Using `docker ps`, I can identify containers belonging to the `DMarket-Bot` stack, which is critical. Next up, I plan to capture the container statistics. I will then use `docker stats --no-stream` for a snapshot of CPU and RAM usage.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"Окей, я оценю производительность вашего Docker-стека для DMarket-Bot. Начну с получения списка запущенных контейнеров, чтобы понять, какие сервисы активны.","textSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1770838033837_22","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker ps"}}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-2.5-pro","usage":{"input":5900,"output":262,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":6162,"cost":{"input":0.0073750000000000005,"output":0.0026200000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770838004728}}
