{"type":"message","id":"18d70518","parentId":"13410a94","timestamp":"2026-02-11T19:27:19.977Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Inspecting DMarket-Bot**\n\nI've begun by checking the active Docker containers using `docker ps`. The initial assessment reveals no running containers, just the table headers. This necessitates further investigation. I'll now examine the Docker Compose configuration to understand the intended setup.\n\n\n**Evaluating Current State**\n\nMy initial check revealed no running containers via `docker ps`, a significant observation. The system seems inactive, which presents the first performance bottleneck. I'm now composing a concise report for the user, highlighting this key finding and seeking clarification on the expected state of the DMarket-Bot. If active operation is desired, I'll then delve into the underlying configurations, including Docker Compose, and attempt to resolve this operational hurdle.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"Похоже, на данный момент нет ни одного запущенного Docker-контейнера. Это и есть первая и главная находка: сервисы DMarket-Bot сейчас неактивны.\n\nВы ожидали, что они будут запущены?\n\nЕсли да, я могу попробовать запустить их и продолжить анализ производительности. Для этого мне нужно будет посмотреть на ваш `docker-compose.yml`.","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-2.5-pro","usage":{"input":6109,"output":323,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":6432,"cost":{"input":0.007636250000000001,"output":0.0032300000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010866250000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770838034068}}
